Balentine is an employee-owned wealth management firm headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia, with an additional office in Raleigh, North Carolina. We provide investment management and financial planning services for high-net-worth individuals and families. At Balentine, we get to know and understand the unique needs of each of our clients. In today’s rapidly changing world, a holistic approach and uncommon agility are required to capitalize on opportunities, and we have built our firm around these enduring ideas. We build long-term relationships with our clients, and we seek to deliver exceptional client service along with consistent long-term investment returns.



What We Believe





 

					
											We believe in investing a great deal of time to get to know you					
									



 

					
											We believe in mastering the details					
									



 

					
											We believe we have designed the right business model to serve our clients					
									




 

					
											We believe risk management matters					
									



 

					
											We believe investment discipline is essential to success					
									



 

					
											We believe serving clients is more important than gathering assets					
									






